snippet.title: Longplay of Phantasy Star Online Episode I & II (Plus) (Episode I - 1/2) [Old]
snippet.description:
Longplay of Phantasy Star Online Episode I & II Plus, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Sep. 15th, 2004. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Episode 1 (2/2): https://youtu.be/eK267MW3QFo
Episode 2: https://youtu.be/JDsBDUv6B8g
